1. User opens PropertyPanel → RuleBuilder accordion → Add/edit rules with visual UI
2. Rules saved in element.visibilityRules array in formStore
3. At runtime (PreviewPage), evaluateRulesForElement() checks each element's rules against current form data
4. Elements are shown/hidden or enabled/disabled based on evaluation result
